<name>Sprite Scaling</name>
<group>moan</group>
<synopsis>Returns true if a sprite is scaling</synopsis>
<syntax><i>scaling</i> = Sprite Scaling (<i>spriteNum</i>)</syntax>
<desc>
Tests if a moan sprite scale started with the @@Scale Sprite@@ command has finished.

Sets <i>scaling</i> to true if the scale of sprite <i>spriteNum</i> is still on going, and false if it has finished.
</desc>
